@DATABASE "Power Drift"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - P - Power Drift"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - P
                   ====================================

                                Power Drift
                                ===========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Credits" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(47223,0)"}        47223,0
@{"Always Qualify  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(47242,0)"}        47242,0
@{"Credits = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(54010,255)"}        54010,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.

@endnode
